Sentencas: Electrochemical impedance measurements were carried out on symmetrical nickel/gadolinia-doped ceria test cells.
Titulo: Diffusion Impedance on Nickel/Gadolinia-Doped Ceria Anodes for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: For H(2), N(2), and H(2)O mixtures, the diffusion length obtained based on the impedance measurements is on the order of centimeters.
Titulo: Diffusion Impedance on Nickel/Gadolinia-Doped Ceria Anodes for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: This high value of the diffusion length is attributed to the flow field in the reactor.
Titulo: Diffusion Impedance on Nickel/Gadolinia-Doped Ceria Anodes for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: It is suggested that a detailed analysis of the gas flow field inside the test reactor is essential before interpreting the impedance measurements with various solid oxide fuel cell test configurations.
Titulo: Diffusion Impedance on Nickel/Gadolinia-Doped Ceria Anodes for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
